        "created_at": "2025-07-31T15:58:46.369Z",
        "cooked": "<p><strong>1975 Sterling Vineyards Cabernet Sauvignon Napa Valley</strong></p>\n<p>Opened by Allred at his 50th birthday dinner. Made by the founding winemaker Ric Forman. 2 bottles were opened and the first was maderized. Decanted for sediment before drinking. This bottle showed very well. Smooth and elegant. Notes of dried mushrooms, wet earth and red berries. Integrated tannins. I liked this better than the 1975 Beau-Sejour Becot which was also opened. 91-92 points.</p>\n<p>VM<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/original/4X/4/f/3/4f3fe6da428f649b38fb5d1fa62b0e1acc84bbe0.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/4f3fe6da428f649b38fb5d1fa62b0e1acc84bbe0\" title=\"IMG_5069\"><img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/4X/4/f/3/4f3fe6da428f649b38fb5d1fa62b0e1acc84bbe0_2_247x500.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG_5069\" data-base62-sha1=\"bj4D09pw5jSEqTPvgupljirZune\" width=\"247\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/4X/4/f/3/4f3fe6da428f649b38fb5d1fa62b0e1acc84bbe0_2_247x500.jpeg, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/4X/4/f/3/4f3fe6da428f649b38fb5d1fa62b0e1acc84bbe0_2_370x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/4X/4/f/3/4f3fe6da428f649b38fb5d1fa62b0e1acc84bbe0_2_494x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"969679\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_5069</span><span class=\"informations\">567\u00d71144 131 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
